<h2>PGP Challenge</h2>
<p>Decrypt the following message with your private key and paste the plaintext code below:</p>
<pre><%= @encrypted %></pre>
<form method="post">
  <input type="text" name="code" placeholder="Paste decrypted code" size="40" required autocomplete="off">
  <button type="submit">Verify</button>
</form>
<p><small>Note: This form uses cryptographic verification instead of CSRF tokens.</small></p>
